Sentencas: In this study, we prepare Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta (BSCF) cathodes using the reactive sintering method.
Titulo: Low-temperature fabrication of (Ba,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 cathode by the reactive sintering method

Sentencas: BSCF is known as a candidate for cathode material of intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cell.
Titulo: Low-temperature fabrication of (Ba,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 cathode by the reactive sintering method

Sentencas: This BSCF cathode is fabricated on the anode supported cells at a low-temperature of 700 degrees C in order to overcome a crystal phase transition from cubic to hexagonal.
Titulo: Low-temperature fabrication of (Ba,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 cathode by the reactive sintering method

Sentencas: Utilizing the reactive sintering, hexagonal BSCF cathode can be synthesized and sintered at 700 degrees C by using the intermediate compound of BSCF.
Titulo: Low-temperature fabrication of (Ba,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 cathode by the reactive sintering method

Sentencas: In addition, the reactive sintering can improve the sinterability of BSCF and decrease the ohmic and polarization resistances of the cells.
Titulo: Low-temperature fabrication of (Ba,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 cathode by the reactive sintering method

Sentencas: The anode supported cell having hexagonal BSCF cathode shows a good power output, compared with the sample made from a commercial cubic BSCF powder.
Titulo: Low-temperature fabrication of (Ba,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 cathode by the reactive sintering method

Sentencas: It is considered that the reactive sintered BSCF cathode layer has a good interface with gadolinium doped ceria interlayer.
Titulo: Low-temperature fabrication of (Ba,Sr)(Co,Fe)O3 cathode by the reactive sintering method

Sentencas: It is found the hexagonal BSCF has good cathode properties if the cathode sintered well at low-temperature.
